{"tid":2405630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門醫院男病人一度失蹤　倒卧院外路邊搶救後不治　消息：疑自高處墮下","createTime":"2021-02-12T13:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T13:50:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a496f33129eb463922ac1458633d9f63af4bee6c","tid":2405630,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:42:27.000Z","msg":"醫院管理局今（12 日）傍晚發稿指，屯門醫院一名 32 歲男病人今早 8 時許，被發現不在病房，數分鐘後被發現倒臥院外數分鐘路程的路邊，搶救後不治。院方將成立委員會調查事件，個案已轉交死因裁判官跟進。消息指，男病人來自內科病房，懷疑由高處墮下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E7%94%B7%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4-%E5%80%92%E5%8D%A7%E9%99%A2%E5%A4%96%E8%B7%AF%E9%82%8A%E6%90%B6%E6%95%91%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E7%96%91%E8%87%AA%E9%AB%98%E8%99%95%E5%A2%AE%E4%B8%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4-%25E5%2580%2592%25E5%258D%25A7%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2582%258A%25E6%2590%25B6%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%2587%25AA%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E4%25B8%258B%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=eca1d6e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4-%25E5%2580%2592%25E5%258D%25A7%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2582%258A%25E6%2590%25B6%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%2587%25AA%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E4%25B8